    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Refresh and maintain neoprene gear with Revivex Wetsuit and Drysuit Shampoo. Expensive suits are prone to chlorine and salt damage after years of use. This gentle shampoo washes and conditions suits by removing organic residues as well as algae and bacteria. After using this cleaner, neoprene gear smells fresh, stays supple and lasts much longer. It’s also ideal to use on neoprene booties, gloves, fishing waders and GORE-TEX drysuits and paddle jackets. Choose the B.C.D. Deluxe Kit to extend the life of scuba equipment and accessories including plastic and rubber parts, interior lining, hoses and valves. Revivex B.C.D. Cleaner is a low-suds formula that’s also a silicone conditioner</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-repeat