r -->\n\t      <div class=\"navbar navbar-default\" role=\"navigation\">\n\t        <div class=\"container\">\n\t          <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n\t            <!-- ADD YOUR SELLER NAME OR LOGO HERE -->\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/irongateamericansupply\">Irongate American Supply</a>\n\t          </div>\n\t          <div class=\"navbar-collapse collapse\">\n\t            <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n\t\t      <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/irongateamericansupply\">Our eBay Store</a></li>\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/irongateamericansupply?_trksid=p2047675.l2559\">About Us</a></li>\n\t              <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/contact/sendmsg?&recipient=irongateamericansupply\">Contact Us</a></li>\n\t            </ul>\n\t          </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n\t        </div>\n\t      </div>\n\n\n\t      <div class=\"container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"main-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/gear_repair/gear_aid_30141_main.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t          <h1>GEAR AID Wetsuit Cleaner and Conditioner for Neoprene, Concentrated, Odor Kit</h1>\n\t\t\t  <h2>MSRP 29.99</h2>\n\t\t\t  <h3>GEAR AID</h3>\n\t          <p>Refresh and maintain neoprene gear with Revivex Wetsuit and Drysuit Shampoo. Expensive suits are prone to chlorine and salt damage after years of use. This gentle shampoo washes and conditions suits by removing organic residues as well as algae and bacteria. After using this cleaner, neoprene gear smells fresh, stays supple and lasts much longer. It’s also ideal to use on neoprene booties, gloves, fishing waders and GORE-TEX drysuits and paddle jackets. Choose the B.C.D. Deluxe Kit to extend the life of scuba equipment and accessories including plastic and rubber parts, interior lining, hoses and valves. Revivex B.C.D. Cleaner is a low-suds formula that’s also a silicone conditioner. All Revivex cleaners, when used with Revivex Odor Eliminator, can also kick lingering mildew or urine smells to the curb. For costly dive suits and equipment that need a little cleaning and refreshing, use Revivex formulas to do the job right.</p>\n\n\n\t\t\t  <h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t  <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t  <div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t  <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">MCN</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">21563301410</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Clean and condition neoprene wetsuits, drysuits, booties and life jackets with Revivex Wetsuit and Drysuit Shampoo; removes salt, algae, bacteria, and chlorine</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Extend suit life by keeping neoprene supple and fresh while protecting against fading, dryness, and premature aging; 10 fl oz size includes 10 washes</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Treat stubborn mold, mildew, urine or pet smells with Revivex Odor Eliminator, a powerful, natural formula; 10 fl oz size includes 20 washes</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Remove damaging salt crystals, chlorine, and organic residue from scuba equipment with Revivex B.C.D. Cleaner, a concentrated formula in a 10 fl oz pouch that’s good for 10 washes</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Apply Revivex Odor Eliminator as a spray, soak or add it to a machine wash to refresh base layers, activewear, outerwear, cycling gear, tents and more</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n              <table>&nbsp;</table>\n              </div>\n  </body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
